</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">That'll Be the Day</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div role="note" class="hatnote">This article is about the Buddy Holly song. For the 1958 album, see <a href="/wiki/That%27ll_Be_the_Day_(album)" title="That'll Be the Day (album)">That'll Be the Day (album)</a>. For the 1973 film, see <a href="/wiki/That%27ll_Be_the_Day_(film)" title="That'll Be the Day (film)">That'll Be the Day (film)</a>. For the UK theatre show, see <a href="/wiki/That%27ll_Be_the_Day_(musical)" title="That'll Be the Day (musical)">That'll Be the Day (musical)</a>.</div>
